description_0: A low angle view of a white contrail extending from the bottom right to the top left corner of the image. The contrail is intersecting the sun in the middle of the image. There is a cirrus cloud covering the majority of the sky in the image. The sun and the contrail can be seen through the cloud.
description_1: In the blue sky there is a thick contrail cloud pattern through the middle and cirrus clouds below them. A tree top is peaking through the bottom right corner and a smaller tree showing on the left bottom corner.
